    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，毫秒级，axisFormat用%ms。到达事件很重要，单独放一个Llegadas区域，把P1_arrive、P2-T1_arrive这些都做成里程碑节点。P1在0时刻最先到达。",
      "elements_involved": [
