      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建骨架：标题定为'Planificación RR (Retail_PointOfSale) - Hilos Mixtos - Parte 1'，四个section——P1、P2、P3和Llegadas。P1区域先放上P1-T1_exec，标记为active状态，0到4毫秒。",
